{"title":"Random case for letters in the text","description":"This tool converts the letter case of your text or part of it to random, part of the letters will be converted to uppercase, part to lowercase","content":"## Converting the letter case to random\r\nThis tool converts the letter case of your text or part of it to random: part of the letters will be converted to uppercase, part to lowercase. In order to select a section of the text to be converted, it is necessary to select it in the text field.\n\n You can also familiarize yourself with other functionality of this online [text editor](/en/editor)."}